        "Cat"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，Do work: 1: Me, Cat。那整个journey的结构就是：标题My working day，一个section叫Go to work，里面三个步骤，分数和参与者都确定了。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
